1
00:00:04,407 --> 00:00:07,641
Ted, if you had three wishes,
what would they be?

2
00:00:07,647 --> 00:00:10,400
Three wishes? I don't know, really.

3
00:00:10,447 --> 00:00:13,325
I suppose
the first one'd be world peace,

4
00:00:13,367 --> 00:00:16,200
and then maybe an end to hunger

5
00:00:16,247 --> 00:00:18,124
and, er…

6
00:00:18,167 --> 00:00:20,044
(Disco music)

7
00:00:21,407 --> 00:00:25,002
more money for hospitals
and that type of thing.

8
00:00:25,047 --> 00:00:26,639
Fair enough, Ted.

9
00:00:26,687 --> 00:00:29,007
And what would your three wishes be?

10
00:00:29,047 --> 00:00:31,481
Oh, no, I'm happy enough, really.

11
00:00:31,527 --> 00:00:34,727
–You wouldn't want anything?
–No, I don't think so.

12
00:00:34,767 --> 00:00:37,281
I can't think of anything, anyway.

13
00:00:38,767 --> 00:00:42,167
You wouldn't, say, want a big car
to drive around in?

14
00:00:42,207 --> 00:00:44,198
Oh-ho, wow!

15
00:00:44,247 --> 00:00:46,124
That'd be fantastic!

16
00:00:46,167 --> 00:00:49,477
Driving around in a big car—
that'd be brilliant!

17
00:00:49,527 --> 00:00:51,518
(Panting)

18
00:00:53,767 --> 00:00:55,767
What would be your second wish?

19
00:00:55,807 --> 00:00:58,315
Oh, that'd be fine.
The car'd be fine.

20
00:00:58,327 --> 00:01:02,764
You wouldn't like to be a rock star
or something, like Elvis?

21
00:01:02,807 --> 00:01:04,604
Oh-ho, God, yeah!

22
00:01:04,647 --> 00:01:07,807
I'd love to be a rock star
like Elvis or something!

23
00:01:07,847 --> 00:01:09,644
That'd be brilliant!

24
00:01:13,087 --> 00:01:16,124
So, uh, your third wish,
if you had one?

25
00:01:16,167 --> 00:01:17,759
Oh, no, that'd be fine.

26
00:01:17,807 --> 00:01:21,173
If I had a big car
and I was Elvis that'd be grand.

27
00:01:23,367 --> 00:01:25,278
You wouldn't like, say, um…

28
00:01:26,327 --> 00:01:27,760
this cup?

29
00:01:27,807 --> 00:01:29,798
Oh, God, yeah!

30
00:01:30,967 --> 00:01:32,719
I'd love that cup!

31
00:01:32,767 --> 00:01:37,255
If I had that cup and I was Elvis
in a big car, that'd be fantastic!

32
00:01:38,487 --> 00:01:41,399
You've never had
much imagination, have you?

33
00:01:41,447 --> 00:01:43,244
You're right there, Ted.

